{"title":"第一周课程-基础概念","uid":"931cb9b0b0328ab44d5960fb6d8e6b9f","slug":"第一周课程-基础概念","date":"2024-01-23T13:58:46.000Z","updated":"2024-01-26T08:02:44.530Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/第一周课程-基础概念.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h3 id=\"1-Internet\"><a href=\"#1-Internet\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. Internet\"></a>1. Internet</h3><ul>\n<li><p><strong>发展阶段</strong>:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>静态页面时期:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>仅浏览网页</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>引入多媒体技术</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>多媒体技术</strong>就是通过计算机对<strong>各种信息</strong>(语言文字 、数据、音频、视频等)进行存储和管理，使用户能够通过<strong>多种感官</strong>跟计算机进行<strong>实时信息交流</strong>的技术</p></blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>CGI阶段</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>CGI</strong>: Common Gateway Interface(通用网关接口), 是WWW技术中最重要的技术之一, 是外部应用程序(即CGI程序)与WEB服务器之间的接口标准, <strong>负责在CGI程序和Web服务器之间传递信息</strong></p></blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>云服务时期</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Web技术趋于复杂, 各种技术开始运用, 增加了Web开发运维的难度</li>\n<li>云服务发展, 部署环境容器化, 功能拆分</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-网络安全\"><a href=\"#2-网络安全\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 网络安全\"></a>2. 网络安全</h3><ul>\n<li><p><strong>Web安全</strong>（Web Security）</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>定义: 保护网络基础设施, 信息系统, 用户数据防止非法访问, 窃取和破坏的措施(or: 专注于保护互联网上的Web应用程序和网站的安全性)</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>WEB</strong>，一种分布式<strong>图形信息系统</strong>。是建立在Internet上的一种网络服务，为浏览者在Internet上查找和浏览信息提供了图形化的、易于访问的<strong>直观界面</strong></p></blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-专业术语\"><a href=\"#3-专业术语\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 专业术语\"></a>3. 专业术语</h3><ul>\n<li><p><strong>IP地址</strong>（Internet Protocol Address，互联网协议地址）</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>在互联网上<strong>唯一</strong>标识和定位计算机&#x2F;设备的<strong>数字地址</strong>, 通常是IPv4(32位, 如192.168.5.130)或IPv6(128位, 如fe80::fe44:e504:6d2a:8e01)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>IPv4地址的分类</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>A类地址</strong>: 1.0.0.0 ~ 126.255.255.255, 用于大型网络，支持大量主机</li>\n<li><strong>B类地址</strong>: 128.0.0.0 ~ 191.255.255.255, 于中等规模的网络</li>\n<li><strong>C类地址</strong>: 192.0.0.0 ~ 223.255.255.255, 用于小型网络</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><p>保留私有IP(内网)分类</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>A类</strong>: 10.0.0.0 ~ 10.255.255.255</li>\n<li><strong>B类</strong>: 10.0.0.0 ~ 10.255.255.255</li>\n<li><strong>C类</strong>: 10.0.0.0 ~ 10.255.255.255</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><ul>\n<li><p>这些<strong>私有IP地址</strong>通常用于内部网络，例如家庭网络、企业内部网络或组织内部网络</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>设备在这些私有地址范围内通信时，其流量不会直接在公共互联网上传输，而是通过网络地址转换（NAT）等技术，将私有IP地址<strong>映射</strong>到公共IP地址以便于与互联网通信，提高通信的安全性，助于缓解IPv4地址枯竭的问题</p>\n</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>DNS</strong>(Domain Name System, 域名系统):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>作用:将人类可读的<strong>域名</strong>映射到<strong>IP</strong>地址</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/23/x3w5U.png\" alt=\"image-20240123193146693\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>URL</strong>(Uniform Resource Locator, 统一资源定位符)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>用于指定资源的位置和访问方式</li>\n<li>格式: 协议:&#x2F;&#x2F;地址:端口&#x2F;路径&#x2F;…..</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>安全基础-基本概念</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>黑客</strong>: 研究突破计算机安全系统的人员<ul>\n<li>黑帽黑客: (<strong>非法</strong>)入侵他人的安全系统</li>\n<li>白帽黑客: (<strong>合法</strong>)调试分析安全系统</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>渗透测试</strong>: (合法)<strong>授权</strong>的安全评估方法<ul>\n<li>模拟潜在攻击者的行为, 测试安全性</li>\n<li>作用: 发现和修复潜在安全漏洞</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>攻防演练</strong>(护网行动):<ul>\n<li>各单位, 企业模拟真实情境, 对网络安全系统进行攻击测试和防御</li>\n<li>红队: 模拟攻击方, 在合法, 授权下进行攻击</li>\n<li>蓝队: 复制防御和维护网络安全, 与红队形成对抗</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>网络安全工具</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>IDS</strong>(Intrusion Detection System, 入侵检测系统)</li>\n<li><strong>IPS</strong>(Intrusion-prevention system, 入侵防御系统)</li>\n<li><strong>VPN</strong>(Virtual Private Network, 虚拟专用网络):<ul>\n<li>建立加密通信通道, 使数据传输更加安全</li>\n<li>可为企业提供安全的远程访问, 让远程用户连接访问企业内网</li>\n<li>允许用户模拟位于其他地理位置, 以绕过地理限制</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>防火墙</strong>(Firewall): 一种网络安全设备或软件, 用于监控计算机网络中的数据流量，以防止未经授权的访问、攻击或恶意活动, 是<strong>网络安全的第一道防线</strong></li>\n<li><strong>蜜罐</strong>(Honeypot):是一种安全机制, 用于诱导攻击, 以便监测、分析和学习攻击行为</li>\n<li><strong>补丁</strong>(Patch):修复安全漏洞等问题的解决方案</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>加密技术</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><strong>加密</strong> <strong>解密</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>加密算法: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>对称加密:</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/23/x35mD.png\"></li>\n<li>非对称加密:</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/01/23/x3Yco.png\"></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>安全防护策略</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>身份认证</strong>(Authentication): 验证用户提供的身份信息</li>\n<li><strong>授权</strong>(Authorization):</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>攻击技术</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>恶意软件</strong>*Malware):常见的形式有:<strong>病毒</strong>（Viruses） <strong>蠕虫</strong>（Worms）<strong>木马</strong>（Trojan Horse）<strong>间谍软件</strong>（Spyware）<strong>广告软件</strong>（Adware）</li>\n<li><strong>钓鱼攻击</strong>:(Phshing Attack) :通过欺骗手段获取用户敏感信息<ul>\n<li>攻击者通常伪装成可信赖实体(比如xx官方网站)，诱使用户提供个人信息</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>后门</strong>(Backdoor): 通过绕过正常授权机制而偷偷进入计算机系统或网络的手段</li>\n<li><strong>病毒</strong>: 感染计算机<strong>系统</strong>并传播自身, 可以对生产环境造成大范围破坏</li>\n<li><strong>漏洞</strong>: 软件硬件或系统存在的安全缺陷或错误, 可能被攻击者利用</li>\n<li><strong>社会工程</strong>(Social Engineering): 通过心理学手段, 诱导人们透露敏感信息(很多电信诈骗就是靠的这个)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","text":"1. Internet 发展阶段: 静态页面时期: 仅浏览网页 引入多媒体技术 多媒体技术就是通过计算机对各种信息(语言文字 、数据、音频、视频等)进行存储和管...","permalink":"/post/第一周课程-基础概念","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"网络安全","slug":"网络安全","count":21,"path":"api/tags/网络安全.json"},{"name":"学习日志","slug":"学习日志","count":21,"path":"api/tags/学习日志.json"},{"name":"视频会议","slug":"视频会议","count":4,"path":"api/tags/视频会议.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-Internet\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. Internet</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. 网络安全</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%AF%E8%AF%AD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3. 专业术语</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Myprefer","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/d195051819ce742212020a79d768fb6c?size=256&cache=1710768150791","link":"https://github.com/Myprefer","description":"web security learner, ML learner","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"小迪安全 P1","uid":"fce12428790cc03c0af9eadde9ff43b2","slug":"小迪安全-P1","date":"2024-01-24T03:42:56.000Z","updated":"2024-01-26T13:55:40.548Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/小迪安全-P1.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"1. 渗透测试常用专有名词 POC: Proof of Concept, 概念验证, 指一段漏洞验证代码 EXP: Exploit. 利用, 指利用系统漏洞进行...","permalink":"/post/小迪安全-P1","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":967,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"网络安全","slug":"网络安全","count":21,"path":"api/tags/网络安全.json"},{"name":"学习日志","slug":"学习日志","count":21,"path":"api/tags/学习日志.json"},{"name":"小迪安全","slug":"小迪安全","count":8,"path":"api/tags/小迪安全.json"},{"name":"基础入门","slug":"基础入门","count":5,"path":"api/tags/基础入门.json"}],"author":{"name":"Myprefer","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/d195051819ce742212020a79d768fb6c?size=256&cache=1710768150791","link":"https://github.com/Myprefer","description":"web security learner, ML learner","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{}}